1. *Užasna* sam se uplašila kad sam videla pauka. (I got terribly scared when I saw a spider.)
2. To je *užasno* loša ideja, ne treba ni pokušavati. (That's an awfully bad idea, we shouldn't even try.)
3. Ona je *užasno* talentovana za muziku. (She's terribly talented in music.)
4. Znam da je to *užasno* teško, ali moramo se suočiti sa tim. (I know it's terribly hard, but we have to face it.)
5. Bio je *užasno* umoran posle dugog dana na poslu. (He was terribly tired after a long day at work.)
6. *Užasna* je gužva u gradu u ovo doba godine. (The traffic in the city is terribly congested this time of the year.)
7. *Užasne* vesti su stigle iz zemlje u ratu. (Terrible news arrived from the war-torn country.)
8. Ova hrana ima *užasan* ukus, ne mogu da je jedem. (This food has a terrible taste, I can't eat it.)
9. *Užasno* je da ljudi još uvek ne shvataju ozbiljnost pandemije. (It's terrible that people still don't realize the seriousness of the pandemic.)
10. Videla sam *užasnu* nesreću na putu, bilo je jako strašno. (I witnessed a terrible accident on the road, it was very scary.)